metadata.name: Moneybears Prereveal
metadata.description: MoneyBearClub (MBC) is an American Sweepstakes NFT project that provides amazing utilities for its holders. MBC will be creating a multiplayer open-world racing game within the Metaverse. MBC Play to Earn (P2E) will allow holders to win vehicles monthly by playing the game which will include a race track within the metaverse. MBC currently has 1,666 whitelist spots. If you are able to achieve a position within the whitelist, we are giving away 4 vehicles to 4 lucky whitelist minters. If you mint a bear with a key fob in the mouth you will automatically win a car!
